  17 Aug 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  -monodevelop-0.5.1-r3.ebuild, -monodevelop-0.6.ebuild:
  Remove some older versions.

  05 Jun 2005; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  03 Jun 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Fix problem with shared mime info getting corrupted after an install.

  01 Jun 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.6.ebuild:
  Fix the deps to pull in a version of gtk-sharp that actually works. See bug
  #93472.

  23 May 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.6.ebuild,
  monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Add missing gnome-sharp dep.

  22 May 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Fix deps to be more accurate.

  21 May 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  monodevelop-0.5.1-r3.ebuild, monodevelop-0.5.1-r4.ebuild:
  Mark 0.5.1* as needing mono-1.0.x. They really don't work with mono-1.1.x.

  21 May 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64.

*monodevelop-0.7 (18 May 2005)

  18 May 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> +monodevelop-0.7.ebuild:
  Bump. Now with ikvm and boo support!

  07 Apr 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> monodevelop-0.6.ebuild:
  Add comment about monodevelop-0.6's inability to handle gtk-sharp-1.0.x
  projects.

*monodevelop-0.6 (02 Apr 2005)

  02 Apr 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> +monodevelop-0.6.ebuild:
  Bump. New release with lots of new features/fixes.

  22 Mar 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  -monodevelop-0.5.1-r1.ebuild, -monodevelop-0.5.1-r2.ebuild,
  monodevelop-0.5.1-r3.ebuild, monodevelop-0.5.1-r4.ebuild:
  Remove a few older versions, and fix *-sharp deps to handle gtk-sharp SLOTs
  properly.

  10 Mar 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  monodevelop-0.5.1-r1.ebuild, monodevelop-0.5.1-r2.ebuild,
  monodevelop-0.5.1-r3.ebuild, monodevelop-0.5.1-r4.ebuild:
  mono moved from dev-dotnet -> dev-lang

*monodevelop-0.5.1-r4 (07 Mar 2005)

  07 Mar 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  +files/monodevelop-0.5.1-iconloader.diff, +monodevelop-0.5.1-r4.ebuild:
  Add a fix for icon loading with some gtk+ themes. See bug #83607. Thanks to
  Alexander Kaiser for the fix.

*monodevelop-0.5.1-r3 (08 Feb 2005)

